snippet: Darren Collison had 22 points in his ninth start of the season, DeMarcus Cousins also scored 22 and the Sacramento Kings completed a four-game season sweep of the Los Angeles Lakers with a 106-98 victory Tuesday night....
lead_paragraph: Darren Collison had 22 points in his ninth start of the season, DeMarcus Cousins also scored 22 and the Sacramento Kings completed a four-game season sweep of the Los Angeles Lakers with a 106-98 victory Tuesday night.

headline.main: Kings Complete First Season Sweep of Lakers, 106-98
headline.print_headline: Kings Complete First Season Sweep of Lakers, 106-98
